moreGigs.title: Summer Festival
moreGigs.venue: The Summer Festival will take place at The Villa@Hoffman Park, a stunning outdoor venue located in the heart of the city. The Villa is a spacious and elegant property that boasts sprawling gardens, tranquil ponds, and plenty of open space for guests to relax and enjoy the festivities.
moreGigs.about: The Summer Festival is an exciting event that takes place every year, showcasing live music, delicious food, and a great atmosphere. This year's festival promises to be one of the best yet, with an impressive lineup of talented musicians and mouth-watering food trucks that will keep your taste buds happy all evening long.

moreGigs.title: Jazz Night at the Park
moreGigs.venue: Join us for Jazz Night at the Park, held at the beautiful Central Park Amphitheater. This outdoor venue is the perfect setting for an evening of live jazz music and good vibes.
moreGigs.about: Jazz Night at the Park is a community event that celebrates the rich history and cultural significance of jazz music. Come out and enjoy a night of smooth tunes, good company, and delicious food from local vendors.

moreGigs.title: Rockin'roleplay
moreGigs.venue: Join us for an evening of head-banging rock music at the City Park Amphitheater. This outdoor venue provides the perfect backdrop for an unforgettable night of music and fun.
moreGigs.about: Rockin' in the Park is an annual event that celebrates the spirit of rock and roll. With a lineup of talented musicians and plenty of food and drink options, this is one summer festival you won't want to miss.

moreGigs.title: Summer Jazz Fest
moreGigs.venue: The Summer Jazz Fest will take place at the beautiful Riverside Park, a lush green space located in the heart of downtown. This scenic outdoor venue is the perfect place to kick back, relax, and enjoy some great jazz music.
moreGigs.about: The Summer Jazz Fest is a celebration of all things jazz. With a lineup of world-class musicians and a wide variety of food and drink options, this event is sure to be a hit with music lovers of all ages.

moreGigs.title: Country Jam
moreGigs.venue: Join us for an evening of country music at the beautiful Lakeside Park. This outdoor venue offers stunning views of the lake and plenty of space to kick up your boots and dance.
moreGigs.about: Country Jam is an annual event that celebrates the best of country music. With a lineup of talented musicians and plenty of food and drink options, this event is the perfect way to spend a summer evening with friends and family.

moreGigs.venue: Get ready to dance the night away at Latin Grooves, held at the spacious and lively Sunburst Park. This outdoor venue provides the perfect setting for a night of hot and spicy Latin music.
moreGigs.about: Latin Grooves is a celebration of the vibrant and exciting world of Latin music. With a lineup of talented musicians and a variety of food and drink options, this event is sure to be a hit with anyone who loves to dance.

moreGigs.about: Classical Serenade is a celebration of the timeless beauty and elegance of classical music. With a lineup of talented musicians and plenty of food and drink options, this event is sure to be a hit with anyone who appreciates the finer things in life.
